id: pm-oslr
title: "Promote execution and diagnostics primitives to the public SDK: linked-test running and test-run lifecycle, search eval harness, telemetry stats/export"
description: "Completes SDK coverage of the command surface beyond pm-oxrw (which covers validate/health/gc only): pm test / test-all execution plus the test-runs worker lifecycle (list/status/logs/stop/resume), the search eval benchmark harness (pm eval, offline BM25 vs provider comparison from PR#314), and telemetry stats/percentiles/export hooks (PR#286, PR#233 OTLP queue). pm-zwpp promotes linked-test STORAGE; this item promotes EXECUTION. The pm-lodl inventory validates this is the final uncovered family. Duplicate check: no open SDK-promotion overlap (searched test/eval/telemetry promote)."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 3
